8/grand-theft-auto-6-hacker.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/grand-theft-auto-6-hacker-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/grand-theft-auto-6-hacker-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/grand-theft-auto-6-hacker-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/grand-theft-auto-6-hacker-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/grand-theft-auto-6-hacker-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3488123" class="wp-caption-text"> “侠盗猎车手5”荣誉：Take-Two Interactive</figcaption></figure><p> WAME与<em>PCGAMESN</em>有关响应情况的以下声明与PCGAMESN联系，并指出：</p><p> “鉴于围绕内德·卢克（Ned Luke）在我们的申请中的声音利用的最新争议，我们希望表达我们深刻的理解和关注。这一事件强调了AI技术的发展与道德和法律领域之间的复杂相互作用。</p><p> WAME致力于保护配音演员和创作者的权利，同时推进道德AI实践。我们认为，这一争议是将AI技术与相关法规协调的关键时刻。”</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bethesda-softworks">贝塞斯达（Bethesda）</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/starfield-promises-biggest-ever-update-3571023">承诺</a>， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/starfield">Starfield</a></em>将在未来几周内获得其“最大”更新，该更新将以100多个修复和改进的空间RPG进行。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/grand-theft-auto-5-star-slams-ai-using-his-voice-i-just-hate-these-fuckers-3571488">“ Grand Theft Auto 5”明星用他的声音猛烈抨击AI：“我只是讨厌这些混蛋”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
